</p>
<h2>Policy Updates</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in regulations, best practices, or service offerings. Any updates will be promptly posted on this page, and we encourage users to review our Privacy Policy regularly to stay informed.</p>

<p>By using our website and services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy and consent to the practices described herein.</p>
